        <title type="html"><![CDATA[mdx 相关]]></title>
        <id>https://lmssee.github.io/日志/mdx 使用</id>
        <link href="https://lmssee.github.io/日志/mdx 使用"/>
        <updated>2025-02-02T00:00:00.000Z</updated>
        <summary type="html"><![CDATA[与 docusaurus 相关的使用说明]]></summary>
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 class="anchor anchorWithStickyNavbar_LWe7" id="description-文件描述">description 文件描述<a href="https://lmssee.github.io/%E6%97%A5%E5%BF%97/mdx%20%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8#description-%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6%E6%8F%8F%E8%BF%B0" class="hash-link" aria-label="description 文件描述的直接链接" title="description 文件描述的直接链接">​</a></h2>
<p>文件描述用于添加到文件头，展示为当前文件的 <code>name="description"</code> 信息</p>
<h2 class="anchor anchorWithStickyNavbar_LWe7" id="title-标题展示">title 标题展示<a href="https://lmssee.github.io/%E6%97%A5%E5%BF%97/mdx%20%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8#title-%E6%A0%87%E9%A2%98%E5%B1%95%E7%A4%BA" class="hash-link" aria-label="title 标题展示的直接链接" title="title 标题展示的直接链接">​</a></h2>
<p>title 不仅是网页的 title ，也会在<a href="https://lmssee.github.io/%E6%97%A5%E5%BF%97/mdx%20%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8#">侧栏</a>数据缺失时被搜集作为左侧文本展示</p>
<h2 class="anchor anchorWithStickyNavbar_LWe7" id="tags-标签组">tags 标签组<a href="https://lmssee.github.io/%E6%97%A5%E5%BF%97/mdx%20%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8#tags-%E6%A0%87%E7%AD%BE%E7%BB%84" class="hash-link" aria-label="tags 标签组的直接链接" title="tags 标签组的直接链接">​</a></h2>
<p>tags 可用于标记博文或文档，归类。tag 可在根文件下进行管理</p>
<div class="language-yml codeBlockContainer_Ckt0 theme-code-block" style="--prism-color:#393A34;--prism-background-color:#f6f8fa"><div class="codeBlockTitle_Ktv7">docs/tags/yml</div><div class="codeBlockContent_biex"><pre tabindex="0" class="prism-code language-yml codeBlock_bY9V thin-scrollbar" style="color:#393A34;background-color:#f6f8fa"><code class="codeBlockLines_e6Vv"><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">docusaurus</span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">    </span><span class="token key atrule" style="color:#00a4db">label</span><span class="token punctuation" style="color:#393A34">:</span><span class="token plain"> </span><span class="token string" style="color:#e3116c">'建站'</span><span class="token plain"> </span><span class="token comment" style="color:#999988;font-style:italic">#  tag 名，用于展示与该文件关联</span><span class="token plain"></span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">    </span><span class="token key atrule" style="color:#00a4db">permalink</span><span class="token punctuation" style="color:#393A34">:</span><span class="token plain"> </span><span class="token string" style="color:#e3116c">'build_website'</span><span class="token plain"> </span><span class="token comment" style="color:#999988;font-style:italic"># 展示在导航栏</span><span class="token plain"></span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">    </span><span class="token key atrule" style="color:#00a4db">description</span><span class="token punctuation" style="color:#393A34">:</span><span class="token plain"> </span><span class="token string" style="color:#e3116c">"构建网站的相关数据信息"</span><span class="token plain"> </span><span class="token comment" style="color:#999988;font-style:italic"># 标签描述</span><br></span></code></pre><div class="buttonGroup__atx"><button type="button" aria-label="复制代码到剪贴板" title="复制" class="clean-btn"><span class="copyButtonIcons_eSgA" aria-hidden="true"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="copyButtonIcon_y97N"><path fill="currentColor" d="M19,21H8V7H19M19,5H8A2,2 0 0,0 6,7V21A2,2 0 0,0 8,23H19A2,2 0 0,0 21,21V7A2,2 0 0,0 19,5M16,1H4A2,2 0 0,0 2,3V17H4V3H16V1Z"></path></svg><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="copyButtonSuccessIcon_LjdS"><path fill="currentColor" d="M21,7L9,19L3.5,13.5L4.91,12.09L9,16.17L19.59,5.59L21,7Z"></path></svg></span></button></div></div></div>
<h2></h2>]]></content>
