    <entry>
        <title type="html"><![CDATA[相关技术使用]]></title>
        <id>https://lmssee.github.io/日志/相关技术使用</id>
        <link href="https://lmssee.github.io/日志/相关技术使用"/>
        <updated>2025-02-01T00:00:00.000Z</updated>
        <summary type="html"><![CDATA[主要技术 [docusaurus]]]></summary>
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 class="anchor anchorWithStickyNavbar_LWe7" id="主要技术-docusaurus">主要技术 <a href="https://docusaurus.io/zh-CN/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">docusaurus</a><a href="https://lmssee.github.io/%E6%97%A5%E5%BF%97/%E7%9B%B8%E5%85%B3%E6%8A%80%E6%9C%AF%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8#%E4%B8%BB%E8%A6%81%E6%8A%80%E6%9C%AF-docusaurus" class="hash-link" aria-label="主要技术-docusaurus的直接链接" title="主要技术-docusaurus的直接链接">​</a></h2>
<p>构建最最主要的技术当然是框架 <a href="https://docusaurus.io/zh-CN/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">docusaurus</a>。当然，该框架也是需要基础的技术支持：</p>
<ul>
<li><a href="https://www.w3.org/zh-hans/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">html</a>：网页骨架支持。标准由 <a href="https://www.w3.org/zh-hans/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">w3c</a> 提供，学习 <a href="https://developer.mozilla.org/zh-CN/docs/Web/html" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">mdn html</a></li>
<li><a href="https://developer.mozilla.org/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">css</a>： 网页精装必备。标准也有 <a href="https://www.w3.org/zh-hans/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">w3c</a> 提供, 学习可上 <a href="https://developer.mozilla.org/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">mdn css</a></li>
<li><a href="https://tc39.es/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">js</a>：  构建网页多样化、现代化的智能家居。标准由 <a href="https://tc39.es/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">tc39.es</a> 提供， 学习可上 <a href="https://developer.mozilla.org/zh-CN/docs/Web/javascript" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">mdn js</a></li>
<li><a href="https://nodejs.org/zh-cn" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">node</a>： 现代化构建网站的技术</li>
</ul>
<div class="language-ts codeBlockContainer_Ckt0 theme-code-block" style="--prism-color:#393A34;--prism-background-color:#f6f8fa"><div class="codeBlockContent_biex"><pre tabindex="0" class="prism-code language-ts codeBlock_bY9V thin-scrollbar" style="color:#393A34;background-color:#f6f8fa"><code class="codeBlockLines_e6Vv"><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token keyword" style="color:#00009f">import</span><span class="token plain"> </span><span class="token punctuation" style="color:#393A34">{</span><span class="token plain"> BackRipple </span><span class="token punctuation" style="color:#393A34">}</span><span class="token plain"> </span><span class="token keyword" style="color:#00009f">from</span><span class="token plain"> </span><span class="token string" style="color:#e3116c">'oops-ui'</span><span class="token punctuation" style="color:#393A34">;</span><span class="token plain"></span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain"></span><span class="token keyword" style="color:#00009f">const</span><span class="token plain"> a </span><span class="token operator" style="color:#393A34">=</span><span class="token plain"> </span><span class="token number" style="color:#36acaa">1</span><span class="token punctuation" style="color:#393A34">;</span><br></span></code></pre><div class="buttonGroup__atx"><button type="button" aria-label="复制代码到剪贴板" title="复制" class="clean-btn"><span class="copyButtonIcons_eSgA" aria-hidden="true"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="copyButtonIcon_y97N"><path fill="currentColor" d="M19,21H8V7H19M19,5H8A2,2 0 0,0 6,7V21A2,2 0 0,0 8,23H19A2,2 0 0,0 21,21V7A2,2 0 0,0 19,5M16,1H4A2,2 0 0,0 2,3V17H4V3H16V1Z"></path></svg><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="copyButtonSuccessIcon_LjdS"><path fill="currentColor" d="M21,7L9,19L3.5,13.5L4.91,12.09L9,16.17L19.59,5.59L21,7Z"></path></svg></span></button></div></div></div>
<p>Blog posts support <a href="https://docusaurus.io/docs/markdown-features" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Docusaurus Markdown features</a>, such as <a href="https://mdxjs.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">MDX</a>.</p>]]></content>
